<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.269055>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Amynthas quadriorbis sp. nov. Holotype (TESRI-O-H- 47) (voucher number: WH 3 P 1). (a) Ventral view of male pore region (gp, genital papilla; mp, male porophore). (b) Dorsal view of right spermathecae (amp, ampulla; dv, diverticulum). (c) Dorsal view of right prostate gland (pd, prostatic duct). Scale bar 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/269055/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

